{"author":"Sunan Abu Dawud","hadith":{"hadithnumber":3143,"arabicnumber":3143,"text":"। উম্মু আতিয়্যাহ (রাঃ) সূত্রে বর্ণিত। তিনি বলেন, ‘আমরা তার [যয়নাব (রাঃ)] চুলগুলো তিন গোছায় ভাগ করেছিলাম।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (939)"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":55}}}